source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Management Question G2: Where are areas of potential development (e.g., under lease), including renewable energy sites and transmission corridors and where are potential conflicts with CEs?
source.description: This map shows conservation element summaries within areas of potential near-term and long-term energy development.  These summaries help highlight areas of potential conflict between conservation elements and energy development.
